com.google.cloud.compute

Class NetworkInterface.AccessConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.cloud.compute.NetworkInterface.AccessConfig
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    NetworkInterface

    public static final class NetworkInterface.AccessConfig
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Access configuration for a Google Compute Engine instance's network interface. Objects of this class can be used to assign either a static or an ephemeral external IP address to Google Compute Engine instances.
    See Also:
    Static external IP addresses, Ephemeral external IP addresses, Serialized Form
